                            \dfrac{f(x+h)-f(x)}{h}= \frac{(-(x+h)^2+4)-(-x^2+4)}{h}
                        </me>
                        <ol marker="A.">
                            <li>
                                <p>
                                    <m>
                                        \dfrac{x^2 + h^2 +4 -x^2 -4}{h} = \frac{h^2}{h}
