                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p>
                                    <m>
                                        \dfrac{-x^2 - h^2 +4 +x^2 -4}{h} = \frac{-h^2}{h}
                                    </m>
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p>
                                    <m>
                                        \dfrac{-x^2 -2xh - h^2 +4 +x^2 -4}{h} = \frac{-2xh - h^2}{h}
